WEBVTT

1
00:00:06.000 --> 00:00:12.074
Watch Online Movies and Series for FREE
www.osdb.link/lm

2
00:03:23.612 --> 00:03:25.705
Darling. come here.

3
00:03:30.285 --> 00:03:31.343
Do you like it?

4
00:03:40.195 --> 00:03:42.322
Justice...

5
00:03:42.931 --> 00:03:46.298
There will be a trial...

6
00:03:46.468 --> 00:03:51.496
a great trial before a powerful magistrate.

7
00:03:51.807 --> 00:03:54.503
And you. you will be guilty.

8
00:03:55.544 --> 00:03:59.674
Beware! Beware the heat of the fire!

9
00:05:06.348 --> 00:05:11.945
Comrade Chan Gong has come from Beijing.

10
00:05:12.053 --> 00:05:14.385
Welcome her. please.

11
00:05:26.835 --> 00:05:29.531
Comrades. students. revolutionary

12
00:05:29.604 --> 00:05:31.538
companions-in-arms...

13
00:05:31.873 --> 00:05:36.037
I give you my proletarian salute.

14
00:05:42.617 --> 00:05:44.915
I congratulate you on today's grand festival...

15
00:05:44.986 --> 00:05:48.786
for which you have worked so hard.

16
00:05:48.823 --> 00:05:52.088
Your cultural unit has done exceptional work.

17
00:05:57.465 --> 00:06:00.866
I would also like to commend you

18
00:06:00.936 --> 00:06:03.996
on the children's presentation.

19
00:06:04.072 --> 00:06:05.972
It made my heart rejoice.

20
00:06:06.074 --> 00:06:07.632
The story of The Three Heroic Girls...

21
00:06:07.709 --> 00:06:10.507
was a vivid lesson.

22
00:06:10.612 --> 00:06:15.106
It galvanized our historic crusade!

23
00:06:15.583 --> 00:06:21.886
But unfortunately. some efforts
are less successful.

24
00:06:24.459 --> 00:06:30.056
Sometimes the teacher must learn
from his students.

25
00:06:33.435 --> 00:06:34.459
Give it to me.

26
00:06:43.511 --> 00:06:46.605
Capitalist exploitation survived
for centuries...

27
00:06:46.715 --> 00:06:51.118
yet its "classics" are pitiful.

28
00:06:51.386 --> 00:06:54.480
Foreign music is meaningless and empty.

29
00:06:54.556 --> 00:06:57.491
What do they mean by "symphony". "concerto"...

30
00:06:57.525 --> 00:06:59.152
"No 1". "No 2". 'No 3"?

31
00:06:59.427 --> 00:07:01.520
This is empty formalism.

32
00:07:02.030 --> 00:07:04.362
It speaks nothing to the people.

33
00:07:04.466 --> 00:07:07.629
What good is making music... except

34
00:07:07.702 --> 00:07:11.399
to teach and inspire the people?

35
00:07:11.573 --> 00:07:13.063
Long live Chairman Mao!

36
00:07:15.543 --> 00:07:17.511
Overthrow the cultural establishment!

37
00:07:21.916 --> 00:07:23.008
Chou Yuan?

38
00:07:23.118 --> 00:07:24.050
Present.

39
00:07:24.119 --> 00:07:26.747
Why do you teach this instrument?

40
00:07:29.891 --> 00:07:33.349
Comrade Chan Gong. what you say is true...

41
00:07:33.428 --> 00:07:34.918
Louder. please.

42
00:07:37.732 --> 00:07:40.496
Comrade Chan Gong. you are right.

43
00:07:40.769 --> 00:07:44.796
Much of Western music is unrefined. worthless.

44
00:07:45.373 --> 00:07:46.704
This is a fact.

45
00:07:47.742 --> 00:07:49.869
Everything you said is true.

46
00:07:50.145 --> 00:07:51.874
But the music I teach...

47
00:07:52.147 --> 00:07:53.512
Go on!

48
00:07:54.049 --> 00:07:56.950
The music I teach is revolutionary music.

49
00:07:57.419 --> 00:07:59.478
Beethoven. Prokofiev.

50
00:07:59.587 --> 00:08:01.054
Do you think so?

51
00:08:01.790 --> 00:08:04.020
In his speech. Comrade Li said...

52
00:08:04.092 --> 00:08:06.617
Comrade Li was purged and humiliated.

53
00:08:06.694 --> 00:08:09.925
Do you still wish to quote him?

54
00:08:10.999 --> 00:08:12.990
I didn't know.

55
00:08:14.502 --> 00:08:16.902
I have taught for many years.

56
00:08:16.971 --> 00:08:18.529
That is apparent.

57
00:08:19.040 --> 00:08:21.508
We believe in the rule of many voices.

58
00:08:21.709 --> 00:08:24.109
What should we do here?

59
00:08:24.446 --> 00:08:26.073
Throw away that old junk!

60
00:08:26.114 --> 00:08:28.514
Chou Yuan. you must admit your guilt.

61
00:08:28.817 --> 00:08:31.149
Let's challenge degenerate Western art!

62
00:08:32.053 --> 00:08:34.613
Comrade. may I say a few words?

63
00:08:37.425 --> 00:08:38.949
Of course.

64
00:08:40.528 --> 00:08:45.659
Students. comrades. revolutionary Red Guards...

65
00:08:46.601 --> 00:08:49.536
I'm not an authority on foreign music.

66
00:08:49.637 --> 00:08:52.197
I have not studied like Comrade Chan Gong.

67
00:08:52.941 --> 00:08:55.205
But in my opinion. there's nothing

68
00:08:55.443 --> 00:08:58.537
as beautiful as our traditional music.

69
00:08:59.647 --> 00:09:01.740
Chou Yuan also teaches the hu chin.

70
00:09:03.051 --> 00:09:05.519
Could he not focus on that?

71
00:09:12.961 --> 00:09:16.488
Comrade Xiang has shown her wisdom.

72
00:09:22.971 --> 00:09:27.601
Put this down with the other "great olds"!

73
00:09:36.684 --> 00:09:39.881
To every problem there is a solution!

74
00:09:40.021 --> 00:09:42.990
I'm sure you can discover the problems.

75
00:09:43.057 --> 00:09:45.753
And I'm sure you can solve them.

76
00:12:41.903 --> 00:12:44.895
Who is it? Who's there?

77
00:12:51.512 --> 00:12:53.139
Ming!

78
00:12:53.247 --> 00:12:55.408
You scared me. I didn't hear you.

79
00:13:04.859 --> 00:13:07.726
It's a mess. I was tidying up.

80
00:13:07.862 --> 00:13:09.329
What's that?

81
00:13:12.166 --> 00:13:13.895
This is a violin.

82
00:13:14.936 --> 00:13:17.166
A musical instrument from Europe.

83
00:13:17.438 --> 00:13:18.837
From Europe?

84
00:13:19.140 --> 00:13:20.505
Is it a bad thing?

85
00:13:20.775 --> 00:13:25.178
No. a violin itself is a good thing.

86
00:13:25.446 --> 00:13:27.471
Here. take a look

87
00:13:31.119 --> 00:13:33.144
We have to study foreign music

88
00:13:33.488 --> 00:13:35.422
so we can move on...

89
00:13:35.490 --> 00:13:36.718
as Chairman Mao said.

90
00:13:36.791 --> 00:13:39.123
Dad asked if you're coming.

91
00:13:39.227 --> 00:13:40.387
He's waiting.

92
00:13:40.428 --> 00:13:44.091
Yes. Tell him I'll come to see him right away.

93
00:13:44.198 --> 00:13:45.859
As soon as I finish my work.

94
00:13:49.303 --> 00:13:51.794
- Ming?
- Yes?

95
00:13:53.574 --> 00:13:57.908
What you see here. don't tell anyone.

96
00:14:05.219 --> 00:14:06.516
I want you to listen.

97
00:15:01.209 --> 00:15:03.473
This will be our secret. all right?

98
00:15:08.850 --> 00:15:10.147
Go!

99
00:15:36.010 --> 00:15:38.979
Ming!

100
00:15:40.481 --> 00:15:42.005
- Was she home?
- Yes.

101
00:15:42.183 --> 00:15:43.207
Is she coming?

102
00:15:43.284 --> 00:15:45.616
No. she said she'd meet you.

103
00:15:45.853 --> 00:15:48.583
What? Is she coming or not?

104
00:15:48.656 --> 00:15:49.918
I can't say why.

105
00:15:49.991 --> 00:15:50.980
Why what?

106
00:15:51.292 --> 00:15:53.089
I promised her to keep it secret.

107
00:15:53.528 --> 00:15:54.859
What are you saying?

108
00:15:54.929 --> 00:15:58.387
I'm your father. You must tell me everything.

109
00:16:05.907 --> 00:16:07.306
- Xiang Pei!
- Papa. don't!

110
00:16:07.608 --> 00:16:09.132
Open up. it's me.

111
00:16:10.444 --> 00:16:11.570
Where's the key?

112
00:16:12.513 --> 00:16:14.003
Go!

113
00:16:23.991 --> 00:16:25.720
Quiet!

114
00:16:33.901 --> 00:16:35.960
Where is she?

115
00:16:41.609 --> 00:16:43.474
Water! Water!

116
00:16:57.091 --> 00:16:58.080
She's gone.

117
00:17:34.428 --> 00:17:37.056
Is this her?

118
00:17:43.404 --> 00:17:46.430
Look at the date: 1937. It must be her mother.

119
00:18:08.996 --> 00:18:13.023
Chou Yuan!

120
00:18:25.046 --> 00:18:26.673
- What do you want?
- Please let me in.

121
00:18:27.114 --> 00:18:28.604
I've done nothing.

122
00:18:28.716 --> 00:18:30.183
Let me inside.

123
00:18:44.331 --> 00:18:45.491
This is for you.

124
00:18:46.500 --> 00:18:47.694
I don't want it.

125
00:18:57.311 --> 00:18:59.802
It's for you. Take it.

126
00:19:01.749 --> 00:19:05.617
It's a violin. A violin.

127
00:19:05.753 --> 00:19:07.050
I remember.

128
00:19:10.257 --> 00:19:11.724
Do you want it or not?

129
00:19:12.493 --> 00:19:15.326
I'm an old man. but I'm not a fool.

130
00:19:16.063 --> 00:19:17.530
Where are your comrades?

131
00:19:17.665 --> 00:19:19.565
Are they waiting outside?

132
00:19:20.167 --> 00:19:21.395
This isn't a trap.

133
00:19:22.069 --> 00:19:23.366
I've changed.

134
00:19:23.437 --> 00:19:25.803
I don't need it now. I speak from my heart.

135
00:19:26.073 --> 00:19:27.665
Enough!

136
00:19:30.277 --> 00:19:31.801
And I don't need this.

137
00:19:33.447 --> 00:19:35.108
It's from another time.

138
00:19:37.284 --> 00:19:40.344
If you want it. you can have it.

139
00:19:40.588 --> 00:19:43.489
or else no one will.

140
00:19:45.426 --> 00:19:46.916
Do you want it or not?

141
00:19:50.831 --> 00:19:52.526
I've no time!

142
00:19:53.768 --> 00:19:55.133
No more arguments.

143
00:19:58.506 --> 00:20:04.467
Take it! I am a cadre in the Party.

144
00:20:05.312 --> 00:20:06.711
Do you understand?

145
00:20:07.214 --> 00:20:09.478
I can't keep it.

146
00:20:09.850 --> 00:20:13.843
I love the people. Do you understand?

147
00:20:29.203 --> 00:20:30.500
Xiang Pei!

148
00:20:34.241 --> 00:20:36.232
I will keep it safe.

149
00:20:45.686 --> 00:20:47.586
Let's go eat. I'm starving.

150
00:20:48.322 --> 00:20:50.483
Go ahead. I'll wait here.

151
00:20:50.724 --> 00:20:52.419
I'm sure she'll be back.

152
00:22:08.602 --> 00:22:10.365
The last card.

153
00:22:11.472 --> 00:22:13.269
The last card.

154
00:22:21.448 --> 00:22:22.779
Oh. my God!

155
00:22:22.850 --> 00:22:26.445
Courage. madame... Upside down.

156
00:22:26.654 --> 00:22:29.487
At this point in the spread...

157
00:22:29.590 --> 00:22:31.785
it might be good news.

158
00:22:34.595 --> 00:22:37.928
I feel... I feel the fast air

159
00:22:37.998 --> 00:22:40.466
sweeping around you...

160
00:22:40.801 --> 00:22:45.261
carrying you... furious wind...

161
00:22:46.340 --> 00:22:47.739
and then stopping.

162
00:22:56.083 --> 00:23:00.076
Your journey will end. No question. I see it.

163
00:23:00.587 --> 00:23:04.887
One way or another. your travels are over.

164
00:23:07.795 --> 00:23:13.131
And there is trouble in this like always.

165
00:23:15.602 --> 00:23:19.561
But you... you are strong by now...

166
00:23:19.840 --> 00:23:23.071
strong like a tree in the forest.

167
00:23:23.477 --> 00:23:24.808
Where is he?

168
00:23:25.746 --> 00:23:27.145
Upstairs.

169
00:23:34.488 --> 00:23:36.285
You are not alone.

170
00:23:36.357 --> 00:23:40.657
A crowd of forces. friends and family...

171
00:23:40.794 --> 00:23:42.887
enemies. lovers...

172
00:23:43.931 --> 00:23:47.423
You will attract many admirers...

173
00:23:47.634 --> 00:23:49.499
fighting to win your hand.

174
00:23:51.572 --> 00:23:54.541
And money... lots of money.

175
00:23:55.342 --> 00:23:59.005
No. madame. Don't be afraid.

176
00:23:59.913 --> 00:24:07.649
N this card. I see a rebirth.

177
00:24:32.413 --> 00:24:34.347
This is Mr. Morritz. You know...

178
00:24:36.817 --> 00:24:38.478
So you're the expert?

179
00:24:38.685 --> 00:24:39.777
From New York.

180
00:24:41.121 --> 00:24:42.645
Do you know what you're doing?

181
00:27:05.832 --> 00:27:08.232
316-2799

182
00:29:45.025 --> 00:29:51.157
"With all my heart"

183
00:45:02.775 --> 00:45:04.003
RED VIOLIN UNEARTHED

184
00:46:16.882 --> 00:46:18.406
Ladies and gentlemen

185
00:46:18.651 --> 00:46:22.815
Duval's would like to welcome you
to this eagerly awaited event.

186
00:46:22.888 --> 00:46:25.356
Our thanks to the government of China...

187
00:46:25.458 --> 00:46:29.895
for entrusting us with this
marvelous collection.

188
00:46:29.995 --> 00:46:35.058
Thanks too to Madame Leroux who
organized and made possible this auction.

189
00:46:35.634 --> 00:46:41.732
Let me remind you that the conditions
of sale are listed in the catalog.

190
00:50:05.477 --> 00:50:07.001
Wait!

191
00:50:08.247 --> 00:50:09.271
The tag!

192
00:50:16.021 --> 00:50:17.648
I put the tag on myself.

193
00:50:20.192 --> 00:50:21.318
Too late.

194
00:50:29.935 --> 00:50:32.403
Call security.

195
00:54:01.113 --> 00:54:04.082
Madame? Are you all right?

196
00:54:04.817 --> 00:54:07.183
Is everything all right?

197
00:54:10.589 --> 00:54:12.489
Yes. I'm sorry.

198
00:54:15.160 --> 00:54:17.128
You have the visions.

199
00:54:19.631 --> 00:54:21.724
No. I'd better go now.

200
00:54:22.568 --> 00:54:24.263
My husband...

201
00:54:25.838 --> 00:54:28.602
Of course. go to your husband.

202
00:54:34.079 --> 00:54:35.774
Thanks. Cesca.

203
00:54:36.305 --> 00:55:36.247
